#

Crispy Duck Confit with Cherry Gastrique

$35
800 kcal
Difficulty: 75%

Allergens:

DuckCherries

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

DuckGourmetFrench CuisineComfort Food

Description

Succulent duck leg slowly cooked in its own fat, served with a sweet and tangy cherry sauce, accompanied by creamy polenta and sautéed green beans.

Ingredients

  • Duck legs: 4
  • Salt: 2 tablespoons
  • Duck fat: 4 cups
  • Fresh cherries: 1 cup
  • Sugar: 1/2 cup
  • Red wine vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup
  • Green beans: 2 cups
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
